{"tid":2251752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰港龍CEO嘲議員「曱甴」無被炒","createTime":"2020-10-21T04:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T04:37:26.000Z","uid":247463,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa529d78396134465b85c236573b1a63685f699","tid":2251752,"uid":247463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"// 國泰上月在員工守則中新增要求，當中包括禁絕員工參與違法行為、辭退任何損害公司聲譽人士，同時表明員工在工餘時間，亦不能發放任何侵犯同事私隱、構成欺凌或騷擾的社交網絡帖文，違例者可遭解僱。國泰更鼓勵員工「篤灰」向上司匯報有關人等，早前就疑翻舊賬兼以言入罪，解僱包括國泰港龍工會主席施安娜等多名員工。支持民間五大訴求者被炒，惟國泰港龍行政總裁丘應樺就被踢爆，7月時曾在個人Facebook分享「支持香港警察」的帖文，以「笑喊」表情符號，將一則形容議員為「曱甴」的帖文轉載到個人版面。網民籲「篤灰」丘應樺「帶頭違反公司守則」。//<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190905/EG3CR3IYMDWRERIIECBUBLLA6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190905%2FEG3CR3IYMDWRERIIECBUBLLA6E%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a3fb1b3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190905%2FEG3CR3IYMDWRERIIECBUBLLA6E%2F&h=1fe900de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190905/EG3CR3IYMDWRERIIECBUBLLA6E/</a><br />\nCEO好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafc7347c92f8c18920d620161173d4e34647dde","tid":2251752,"uid":228955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"點解留低ou最簡單因為入邊無論管理層大部份都係大陸人"},{"pid":"66890e83c5298990b713afb6e9cb2b89acc9bda0","tid":2251752,"uid":169819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"藍到咁被人炒先係新聞 仲要係ceo咁大粒"},{"pid":"aa329cb947eb4e9c5ba7534e091ed21ddf30f245","tid":2251752,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"港龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5119df81767c77db4109f